description: In today's episode, Andy & DJ discuss a Houston precinct allowing only Democrats to vote, Democrats giving an “A” to Biden’s State of the Union calling to “fund the police”, and CDC releasing international data on myocarditis caused by the mRNA COVID-19 vaccines.
